MUTUAL BENEFIT HEALTH & ACCIDENT ASSOCIATION v. Elmer H. DAVIS. No. 1002. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. March 26, 1934. Dudley, Hyde, Duvall & Dudley, of Oklahoma City, Okl., and G. J. Cleary, P. E. Horan and V. J. Skutt, of Omaha, Neb., for appellant. Mnrrah & Bohanon,. of Oklahoma City, Okl., for appellee.
